}
You can store multiple mocks on the same fixture file.
{
&quot;create&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;: &quot;e2etestBox&quot;},
&quot;boxFruit&quot;:{
&quot;uuid&quot;:&quot;3376339576e33dfb9145362426a33333&quot;,
