...
&quot;lint&quot;: &quot;ng lint&quot;,
...
}
...
}
This will be used as follows:
sh &quot;&quot;&quot;yarn ${lintScript}&quot;&quot;&quot;
testScript: Script for test the application. Defined at package.json
Example (package.json):
{
